    <!-- We will teach you codes step by step guide but first you need to know the basic -->
    <!-- We will start with the "paragraph tags <p></p>" -->


    <!-- These Tags Are Used To Write A Paragraph, Demo is written Below -->
    <p>Hey there buddy!, we use these tags to write paragraph</p>
    
    <!-- now you know how to make paragraph the most easiest part -->

    <!-- now its a part to understand the tags of html -->

    <!-- down below are the tags that are important to understand -->
    <p>This is a paragraph tag, as we taught you before</p>





    <!-- This is a body tag which you can put all the various elements tags for your website structure
    accordingly as you want it -->
    <body><p>here we have put a paragraph tag in the body</p></body>

    <!-- down below is a html tag, which is used to start to write the structure of your website -->
    <html><body><p>Html is called "Hyper Text Markup Language"</p></body></html>

    <!-- Every tag goes like this way  -->
    <tagname>content goes here...</tagname>



    
    <p>The <!DOCTYPE> declaration represents the document type, and helps browsers to display web pages correctly.

    It must only appear once, at the top of the page (before any TAGS)</p>




    <!--different type of headings  -->

    <!-- These are called headings -->
    <h1>this a heading</h1>
    <h2>this a heading</h2> 
    <h3>this a heading</h3>
    <h4>this a heading</h4>
    <h5>this a heading</h5>
    <h6>this a heading</h6>   



<!-- the given tag below is the <a></a> tag through this you can add links to your website -->
<a href="https://cubeacloud.com">This is a link</a>



